snippet.title: Rangnick's MUFC, Clutch Origi w/ Lawrenson, Rugby w/ Quinlan, Club GAA & Structures, Perf. Rankings
snippet.description:
Ger Gilroy and Eoin Sheahan are live for Monday's OTB AM, after a big weekend of sport that saw Ralf Rangnick get his first win in charge of #MUFC, Leinster get back to winning ways over Connacht, and the #GAA Club Championships heat up.

(01:00) – Kickoff w/ Ger + Eoin
(06:00) – Performance Rankings
8:10am – Football w/ Mark Lawrenson. #LFC, #MUFC
8:30am – Sports Pages + OTB reaction from analyst
8:50am – Rugby w/ Alan Quinlan. #URC
9:10am – #GAA w/ Kevin O’Donovan
9:30am – OTB reaction

#OTBAM is live in association with @Gillette UK | #BestFaceForward
